idan keskin farq qiladi va o&lsquo;z navbatida mehnat bozoridagi jarayonlarga ta&rsquo;sir etadi. Odatda, aholi soni ko&lsquo;p bo&lsquo;lgan hududlarda ishsizlik darajasi ham yuqori bo&rsquo;ladi. Shuningdek, hududlarning mehnat bozorini tavsiflovchi boshqa ko&lsquo;rsatkichlar ham mavjud, masalan, o&#39;rtacha oylik ish haqi, bo&#39;sh ish o&#39;rinlari soni va boshqalar. Hududlarning mehnat bozoridagi vaziyatni tahlil qilish uchun Prognozlashtirish va makroiqtisodiy tadqiqotlar instituti mutaxassislari Hududlar mehnat bozori indeksini (<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">MBI</strong>) hisoblab chiqdi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Mehnat bozori indeksi davlat organlari vakillari, bevosita ish beruvchilar va ish qidiruvchilarga hududlardagi mehnat bozorining joriy holati bo&lsquo;yicha zarur ma&rsquo;lumotni olish imkonini beradi. Demak, indeks quyidagi imkoniyatlarni yaratadi:&nbsp;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">-&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">davlat organlari vakillariga</strong> hududlar bo&lsquo;yicha mehnat bozoridagi holatga baho berish, mehnat bozorining rivojlanishi nuqtai nazaridan hududlarni tasniflash, barqaror vaziyatga erishish uchun zarur chora-tadbirlarni o&lsquo;z vaqtida qabul qilish;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">-&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">ish beruvchilarga</strong> mehnat bozorining holatiga oid tendensiyalarni ko&lsquo;rsatish va shu orqali yangi xodimlarni ishga jalb qilish bo&lsquo;yicha strategiyani to&lsquo;g&lsquo;ri yo&lsquo;nalishga solish;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">- ish qidiruvchilarga</strong> takliflarni qidirish uchun eng qulay davrni tanlash, talab va ish o&lsquo;rinlariga oid o&lsquo;zgarishlarni kuzatib borish va shu orqali ish joyi yoki sohasini o&lsquo;zi uchun foydali tomonga o&lsquo;zgartirishni rejalashtirish.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Indeksni hisoblash</strong> uchun ishsizlik darajasi, mavjud bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rinlari va rezyumelar soni, mehnat bozoridagi konsentratsiya koeffitsiyenti va o&lsquo;rtacha oylik maosh miqdori kabi ko&lsquo;rsatkichlardan foydalanildi.</h3><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(114, 114, 114); text-align: center;"><img height="720" src="https://imrs.uz/public/ckfinder/userfiles/files/uz(15).jpg" width="1280" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: none; height: auto; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 0px; box-shadow: none;" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Barcha ko&lsquo;rsatkichlarni yagona o&lsquo;lchov birligiga keltirishda&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Minimaks va Maksimin usullari</strong>dan foydalanildi. Mazkur usullar 0 dan 100 gacha bo&lsquo;lgan diapazonda ma&rsquo;lumotlarning chiziqli modifikatsiyasini ifodalaydi. Agar indikator qiymatining oshishi ijobiy jarayon bo&lsquo;lsa, Minimaks usuli qo&lsquo;llaniladi, ya&rsquo;ni o&lsquo;zgarishlardan so&lsquo;ng eng kam qiymat 0 ga, eng katta qiymat esa 100 ga teng bo&lsquo;ladi. Indikator qiymatining oshishi salbiy jarayon hisoblangan holatda Maksimin usuli qo&lsquo;llaniladi, ya&rsquo;ni o&lsquo;zgargan ma&rsquo;lumotlar teskari xarakter kasb etadi &ndash; eng kam qiymat 100 ga, eng katta qiymat 0 ga teng bo&lsquo;ladi. Indeksning yakuniy qiymati barcha indikatorlar bo&lsquo;yicha o&lsquo;rtacha arifmetik qiymatni qo&lsquo;llash orqali hisoblanadi.</h3><table style="box-sizing: border-box; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; width: 1140px;"><tbody style="box-sizing: border-box;"><tr style="box-sizing: border-box;"><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Qo&lsquo;shimcha. Foydalaniladigan indikatorlarni asoslash</strong></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><u style="box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Ijobiy indikatorlar:</strong></u></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rinlari soni&nbsp;</strong>ma&rsquo;lum bir xodimga bo&lsquo;lgan talabni ko&lsquo;rsatadi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !importan