g><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">ish</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">o</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&lsquo;</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">rniga</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">o</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&lsquo;</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">rta</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">hisobda</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;5,6&nbsp;</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">ta</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">rezyume</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">to</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&lsquo;</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">g</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&lsquo;</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">ri</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">keladi</strong>. Ishsizlik darajasi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">9,1%&nbsp;</strong>dan oshmaydi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Jizzax, Samarqand, Surxondaryo viloyatlari va Qoraqalpog&lsquo;iston Respublikasi indeks ko&lsquo;rsatkichlari&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">past</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">bo</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&lsquo;</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">lgan</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">hududlar</strong> qatoriga kiradi. Ularda&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">eng</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">yuqori</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">konsentratsiya</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">koeffitsiyenti</strong> kuzatildi, ya&rsquo;ni bitta bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rniga Qoraqalpog&lsquo;iston Respublikasida&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">17,4&nbsp;</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">ta</strong>, Surxondaryoda&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">14,1&nbsp;</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">ta</strong>, Jizzax viloyatida&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">12,0&nbsp;</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">ta</strong> rezyume to&lsquo;g&lsquo;ri keladi. Bu esa mazkur hududlarda ishsizlik darajasining&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">9,3%</strong> gacha yetishi bilan bog&lsquo;liq.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Qashqadaryo viloyatida mehnat bozori&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">indeksi juda past darajada</strong> &ndash;&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2,2</strong> ni tashkil etdi. Buning asosiy sababi har bir bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rniga&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">16,8</strong> nafar talabgor to&lsquo;g&lsquo;ri kelishi va o&lsquo;rtacha oylik maosh respublikadagi o&lsquo;rtacha ko&lsquo;rsatkichdan ancha past ekanligidir.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2021 yil indeks bilan taqqoslash.</strong> Toshkent shahridan tashqari respublikaning barcha hududlarida indeks qiymati&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">pasaygan</strong>. Toshkent shahrida ishsizlik darajasining pasayishi va bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rinlarining ko&lsquo;payishi hisobiga indeks&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">12,9</strong> punktga oshgan. Indeksda Toshkent viloyati Navoiy viloyatidan&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">1,4</strong> ballga o&lsquo;zib ketgan holda ikkinchi o&lsquo;rinni egalladi (2021-yilda Navoiy viloyati 62 ball bilan ikkinchi o&lsquo;rinda edi).&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Konsentratsiya koeffitsiyenti</strong> Toshkent viloyatida&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">1,0 bo&lsquo;lsa,</strong> Navoiyda&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">5,0</strong> tashkil etdi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">2022-yilda Samarqand va Jizzax viloyatlarida bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rinlari soni ish qidirayotganlar sonidan ancha kam bo&lsquo;lganligi bois ko&lsquo;rsatkichlari past hududlar qatoriga kiritildi. Qashqadaryo viloyati juda past darajada joylashdi. Hududda ishsizlik darajasi yuqori, ish haqi mamlakatdagi o&#39;rtacha ko&#39;rsatkichga nisbatan past va bo&#39;sh ish o&#39;rinlari juda kam.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Ikki davr tahlili asosida&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2022</strong>-yilda barcha hududlarda mehnat bozori indeksi (Toshkent shahridan tashqari) pasaygani kuzatildi. Buning asosiy sababi Milliy vakansiyalar bazasida (ish.mehnat.uz) ro&lsquo;yxatdan o&lsquo;tgan rezyumelar soni (o&#39;tgan yildagiga nisbatan 900 ming kishiga ortgan) ko&lsquo;payganligidir. Ushbu tendensiyaga salbiy tomondan ham, ijobiy tomondan ham qarash mumkin.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Salbiy tomoni shundaki, respublikada ishsizlar soni ko&lsquo;p. Ular uchun yangi ish o&lsquo;rinlari yaratilishi kerak, biroq ijobiy tomoni shundaki, aholi faol ish izlay boshladi, mahallalar va hokim yordamchilari faoliyatini yaxshilash bo&lsquo;yicha davlat tomonidan olib borilayotgan chora-tadbirlar ijobiy natijalar bermoqda.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Shunday qilib, umuman olganda, O&lsquo;zbekiston mehnat bozoridagi vaziyat pandemiya davridagiga nisbatan yaxshilanmoqda, ish haqi o oshmoqda. Uning o&lsquo;sish sur&rsquo;ati&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2022-</strong>yilda&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2021-</strong>yildagiga nisbatan&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">121,3</strong>% ni tashkil etdi, ishsizlik&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">0,7%&nbsp;</strong>ga kamaydi. Biroq, shunga qaramay, ishsizlar soni ko&#39;pligini inobatga olgan holda, ayniqsa, ish o&#39;rinlari soni kam bo&lsquo;lgan Qashqadaryo, Surxondaryo viloyatlari va Qoraqalpog&#39;iston Respublikasida yangi ish o&#39;rinlari yaratilishi zarur.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: right;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Muhabbat</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;hmedova,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;">PMTI guruh rahbari</strong></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></div></div><div style="box-sizing: inherit;">&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: inherit;"><i class="bi bi-eye"></i> 2334</span></div></div></div></header></header></header></header></header><div style="box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(114, 114, 114); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><br></div>
